description: Stunning fully renovated multi story two bedroom / 2.5 bathroom condo at the coveted Colony House! Just steps from Colony Square’s shops, restaurants, and entertainment—and a short walk to Piedmont Park, the BeltLine, the High Museum, and the Botanical Gardens—this is city living at its very best.    From the moment you walk in, floor-to-ceiling windows flood the space with natural light and showcase sweeping city views. The spacious living room flows seamlessly into the dining area, while the renovated kitchen features quartz countertops, ample cabinet space, and a brand-new Sub-Zero refrigerator. A stylish half bath completes the main level.    Upstairs, you’ll find a flexible loft space, a guest bedroom perfect for a home office or bedroom, and a spacious owner’s suite with a walk-in closet and a renovated bath.    As part of Colony Square, residents can rent unlimited parking spaces for $150 per car, and the newly reimagined development right outside your door offers top restaurants, IPIC Theater, yoga, spa services, and even a hotel for out-of-town guests.    Don’t miss the chance to live in one of Midtown’s most iconic addresses—this is the perfect blend of style, convenience, and walkability.
